title: 12 Joyful Real Wedding Photos That Are Chock-Full Of Love

organizations.name: seth of vital image 12 r. hickman photography

text:
Punxsutawney Phil saw his shadow on Thursday, so it looks like we’re in for six more weeks of winter ― womp, womp.
But the newlyweds below know that a winter wedding is a wonderful way to counteract a serious case of the seasonal blues. Check out some photos from their sweet celebrations below:
1 Fulleylove Photography/Instagram "This wedding was full of kindness and laughter! And I'm not sure if it gets much better than that!" -- Fulleylove Photography 2 Unashamed Imaging/Instagram "My bride was giving me all the feels! I love that my brides can express how beautiful they are so naturally in front of me." -- Anesha Collins 3 Maral Noori/Instagram "Love the way her hair is hitting her face in the breeze." -- Maral Noori 4 Vesic Photography “Soudeepya and Neel on their wedding night, on the Bay of Bengal at their destination wedding at The Park Hotel in Visakhapatnam, India." -- Hooman Bahrani 5 James Correia/Instagram "First wedding of the year!! Couldn't have asked for better weather in February. And couldn't have asked for a better couple." -- James Correia 6 Rincon Images Wedding Photography "Just after twilight Cara and Blake shared their first dance while the bridal party lit lanterns along the beach in Rincon, Puerto Rico." -- Frances Davis 7 Justine Boulin/Instagram "Maggie and Tony got married last week at Lonsdale Quay." -- Justine Boulin 8 Les Atkins Photography "Hillary and Jake got married this weekend in historic Petersburg, Virginia surrounded by their family and friends." -- Les Atkins 9 Lisa Price Photography "Jordan and Gaby married in Jefferson City, Tennessee." -- Lisa Price 10 Danielle Mahoney Photography "Sheila and Jay had the most beautiful winter wonderland wedding and even got some beautiful snow on their special day, making for some stunning photos at the St. Marys Golf Course in St. Marys, Ontario." -- Danielle Mahoney 11 Trish and Seth of Vital Image "Jordan and Dan got married at Turner Hall in Milwaukee, Wisconsin." -- Trish and Seth of Vital Image 12 R. Hickman Photography "Erin and Darrell's love chased away central Florida's cold front. Their Rockledge Country Club wedding was absolutely stunning." -- Rashad Hickman If you go to a wedding or get married yourself, hashtag your photos #HPrealweddings or e-mail one to us afterward and we may feature it on the site! Please include the couple’s names as well as the date and location of the wedding.
